snippet.description:
soul Interface is an ecosystem simulator that allows players to design artificial lifeforms, train their AI to survive, compete, and cooperate 
in a virtual physics-based environment.

This trailer showcases our plans for the future:
| Physically represented traversable network space with orbital mechanics;
| Customisable destructible player bodies for EVAs;
| Lifeforms spreading to space and onto world' surface;
| Multiplayer with coop-worlds that players can join into constellations - 
to share energy, transfer lifeforms, and create a global ecosystem.

- everything else featured in the trailer is already in the game.

